Sentencas: BaCe0.2Fe0.8-xPrxO3-8 (x = 0?0.3) is studied as a cobalt-free cathode material for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: The cathode is composed of a cubic BaFeO3-8 phase and an orthorhombic BaCeO3-8 phase, and Pr is doped in both phases.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: The partial substitution of Pr for Fe decreases the content of the BaFeO3-8 phase, leading to a lower electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: BaCe0.2Fe0.6Pr0.2O3-8 has the most adsorbed oxygen and Fe3+ on the surface, resulting in the fastest oxygen surface exchange kinetics and the highest activity.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: The partial pressure of H2O shows a negligible effect on the polarization resistance of the cathode.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: In contrast, the polarization resistance increases remarkably with the decrease of oxygen partial pressure, indicating that the rate of the cathode process is controlled by the surface exchange of oxygen.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: At 700 ?C, BaCe0.2Fe0.6Pr0.2O3-8 shows the lowest polarization resistance of 0.057 0
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that Pr doped BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 is a promising cobalt-free cathode material for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Enhanced oxygen reduction reaction activity of BaCe0.2Fe0.8O3-8 cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells via Pr-doping
